Sinisikap kami ng Old Bug na paghiwalayin.

00:28:21.040 --> 00:28:21.910
Pero hindi niya alam

00:28:21.910 --> 00:28:23.830
ang pinagsamahan natin.

00:28:23.830 --> 00:28:25.200
Kung masama kang tao,

00:28:25.550 --> 00:28:26.180
Ako at si Beiming

00:28:26.180 --> 00:28:27.790
namatay na sana ng hindi mabilang na beses.

